Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.81,0:00:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 不要回頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.73,0:00:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 邁步出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.90,0:00:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼淚是閃閃發光的勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.90,0:00:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一步 都化為甘霖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.88,0:00:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight Fight 更加自信了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.41,0:00:36.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要的東西就捨去 這樣也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.50,0:00:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在無限廣闊的心中蔓延開來喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.78,0:00:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於受傷時刻之外　看不見的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.83,0:00:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若現在開始映入雙眸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.78,0:00:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just Try-again
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.11,0:01:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變得強大 抓住機會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.10,0:01:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 無論何時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.11,0:01:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 都要堅信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.14,0:01:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢想絕對能實現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.23,0:01:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有多遙遠 都不害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.23,0:01:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight Fight 更能感覺到明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.31,0:01:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,餵,火美子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.32,0:01:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是很重要的東西啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.32,0:02:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個不好吃呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.15,0:02:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要隨意弄丟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.82,0:02:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子,海火子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.14,0:02:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿瑪,武一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.75,0:02:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家也能把愛找出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.99,0:02:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的只有渡你一個了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.15,0:02:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一定會找到愛給你看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.00,0:02:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼你便去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.47,0:02:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.75,0:02:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,加油啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.24,0:02:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找到愛的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.73,0:02:25.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便能得到松明之火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.62,0:02:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做你自己相信的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.47,0:02:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要幹多餘的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.66,0:02:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.18,0:02:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,加油啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.69,0:02:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三十六話\N展望光輝的明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.01,0:02:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.88,0:02:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到世界的終結去找愛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.55,0:03:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接得好,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.03,0:03:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對,這樣一口氣擲出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.40,0:03:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡真水皮,你自己去拾回來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.14,0:03:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.11,0:03:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.68,0:03:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.27,0:03:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由美…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.35,0:03:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.69,0:03:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.99,0:03:44.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了哪裏呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.36,0:03:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已回去了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.56,0:04:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.75,0:04:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.16,0:04:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒有事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.03,0:05:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.21,0:05:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.07,0:05:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了,快坐上來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.15,0:05:04.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐上去?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.26,0:05:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是最後的貨車了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.85,0:05:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不上去的話便再逃不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.44,0:05:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要逃?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.11,0:05:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不回家的話,媽媽會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.09,0:05:13.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了,已沒時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.91,0:05:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的媽媽一定已乘上別的貨車了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.47,0:05:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可…可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.09,0:05:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在人類想像不到的世界末日已迫近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.80,0:05:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在所有的機場,所有的港口,還有所有的主要公路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.58,0:05:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都充滿了避難的人群
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.00,0:05:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是,在這個地球上還有安全的地方嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.71,0:05:45.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個地球只有被消滅的命運嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.74,0:05:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽吞噬地球的時限已一分一秒的迫近…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.18,0:05:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽吞噬地球?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.37,0:05:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.05,0:05:59.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽吞噬地球是什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.76,0:06:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什麼也不知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.60,0:06:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽突然的膨脹起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.26,0:06:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是,到昨天為止還不是這樣的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.17,0:06:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是被隱藏起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.80,0:06:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.91,0:06:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽變大了會怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.84,0:06:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事也不會發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.07,0:06:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用擔心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.18,0:06:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.83,0:06:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當那太陽西沈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.93,0:06:37.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後再次升起的時候便是末日了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.96,0:06:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們已不能再看見太陽升起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.55,0:06:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎會的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.71,0:06:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傷腦筋了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.11,0:06:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題的,媽媽會在你身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.58,0:06:57.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.12,0:07:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.09,0:07:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.16,0:07:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小朋友,你去哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.34,0:07:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是要回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.49,0:07:10.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽一定是在等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.90,0:07:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.44,0:07:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我住的鎮有這樣的地方嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.17,0:07:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.51,0:07:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.79,0:07:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到剛才為止還是那麼熱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.95,0:09:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是清晨嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.19,0:09:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個海是清晨的海洋嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.63,0:09:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說是黃昏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.10,0:09:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看像哪個?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.40,0:09:30.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔,你為什麼不逃?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.04,0:09:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為畫這幅畫是我的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.10,0:09:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…我想已沒有人會來看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.71,0:09:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.29,0:09:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽會吞噬地球是真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.26,0:09:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又一點也不熱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.43,0:09:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又說太陽不會再升起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.59,0:09:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,升起的時候便是世界末日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.20,0:09:59.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家也是這樣說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.87,0:10:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不,會升起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.10,0:10:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我們不放棄的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.85,0:10:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽一定會升起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.24,0:10:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我深信著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.62,0:10:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那幅畫什麼時候會完成?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.31,0:10:43.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天的清晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.36,0:10:47.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是,為什麼要畫海洋?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.33,0:10:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是我們的故鄉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.25,0:10:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.00,0:10:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們是由海洋孕育出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.80,0:10:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由海洋?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.50,0:10:58.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海洋是生命的起源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.31,0:11:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是從海洋和太陽的力量中得到生命的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.71,0:11:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個太陽為何要把人類…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.78,0:11:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把所有生物消滅呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.59,0:11:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許是因為人類變得太聰明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.74,0:11:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此便開始發怒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.39,0:11:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發怒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.38,0:11:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類開始覺得自己是世上最了不起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.53,0:11:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且什麼也做得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.53,0:11:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類砍下一棵樹會奪去多少生物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.91,0:11:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些事想也沒有想過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.90,0:11:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.68,0:11:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些草、樹木和昆蟲們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.66,0:11:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會都是因為人類而死嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.85,0:11:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣太可憐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.35,0:11:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好的不是人類嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.22,0:11:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是應該更早發現這些事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.15,0:11:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經太遲了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.94,0:11:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.79,0:11:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那數不盡的星星內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.58,0:11:55.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有由今天開始誕生的星星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.52,0:11:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有今日死去的星星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.62,0:11:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死去的星星…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.94,0:12:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是回到了宇宙的自然之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.99,0:12:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這宇宙中…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.41,0:12:05.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有和我們同一命運的星星嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.99,0:12:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定有的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.07,0:12:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後,今後也會是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.53,0:12:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些星星會知道我們的事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.70,0:12:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果知道的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.97,0:12:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便不會再犯同樣的錯誤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.95,0:12:20.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.94,0:12:24.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.25,0:12:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像曾經和叔叔在哪裏見過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.45,0:12:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許會是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.25,0:12:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記不起來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.56,0:12:40.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪裏見過呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.49,0:13:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會滅亡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.73,0:13:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.40,0:13:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們絕對不會滅亡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.47,0:13:20.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信…
